videos.description: Arizona's Ira Lee catches the pass in transition and rocks the rim with a left-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Lee finishes the fast-break flush

videos.description: Arizona's Ira Lee gets big under the basket and makes the double-pump lay-in during the first half against SMU.
videos.headline: Lee hits the double-clutch layup

videos.description: SMU's Jarrey Foster swats away  Allonzo Trier's layup attempt late in the first half.
videos.headline: Foster denies Trier at the rim

videos.description: SMU's Ethan Chargois takes advantage of a second opportunity and makes the layup plus the foul early in the second half against Arizona.
videos.headline: Chargois gets three points the old fashioned way

videos.description: Allonzo Trier tops off Arizona's 13-0 run to take the lead by side stepping a defender for a fast-break layup.
videos.headline: Trier puts the Wildcats back in the lead after Eurostep

videos.description: Deandre Ayton rises up for an offensive rebound, then hammers down a posterizing dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton grabs a rebound and goes back up to the rim with authority
